  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and there was a Jewish soldier [? stuck ?] there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and I was already better, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I could already move.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went to the Jewish soldier, [INAUDIBLE] this friend, was another friend there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, one day, my company came up to Alexandria, and came-- some of my friends came to the-- we met at the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were talking about being shipped to-- being shipped to-- to Italy for the-- for-- for the invasion.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were talking openly about that, even when they are going, and so [? forth. ?]",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said to them, how can you talk about that, I said, openly?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All Alexandria knows already that-- that we-- my company is going on an invasion, and there are spies all over.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How can you talk about it openly like that?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and sure enough, they went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one morning, I woke up in the [? operation ?] camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and [INAUDIBLE] one of my guys that was with me from my company, he came into my tent and said, Willy, 462.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the sea, the Mediterranean, we were torpedoed, the ship sank, and half of my company was lost.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] 148 people were drowned in-- close to Benghazi.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So again, I had-- I had that foresight two times.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] of what happened to me, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And then, when they came back to Egypt after the-- after that-- after that disaster, and the company was reformed, and-- and my company come on-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was very popular in my company.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And even my-- even the officers, although I was only a corporal, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
